Package: fsshap
Type: Package
Title: SHAP-Based Feature Selection with Statistical Significance
Version: 0.1.0
Author: lcuian
Maintainer: lcuian <flystar233@gmail.com>
Description: A package for feature selection based on SHAP (SHapley Additive exPlanations) 
    values and statistical significance testing. Supports regression, binary classification, 
    and multiclass classification tasks. Uses iterative feature reduction to identify 
    statistically significant features.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
